This paper deals with data privacy and access control, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also involves the management and tracking of data, which can be related to database systems (cs.DB). The use of blockchain technology is also a significant aspect of the paper, which can be categorized under cybersecurity (cs.CY). The paper also involves the development of a framework and system, which can be related to software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques to develop a data privacy ontology, which can be related to machine learning (cs.LG).
